PetCalm — Pet Anxiety Assessment & Paid Report Website

Build me a complete, deployable website called PetCalm — an online pet anxiety assessment tool that follows the MBTI business model: free assessment → anxiety profile type result → paid detailed PDF report.

1. CORE CONCEPT
A B2C assessment website targeting dog and cat owners who suspect their pet has anxiety, behavioural issues, or stress. The user answers a structured quiz about their pet's behaviour, environment, and history. At the end, they receive a free summary result — their pet's Anxiety Profile Type — and are offered a paid detailed PDF report with personalised, actionable guidance.
The brand positioning is built on one core reframe: pet anxiety is not a vague worry — it's a diagnosable profile that already exists. The owner just hasn't seen it yet.

